3. âœ… Create/configure 4 custom fields
4. âœ… Scope custom fields to your project only
5. âœ… Add custom fields to project screens
6. âœ… Create 5 Epics
7. âœ… Create 51 Stories linked to Epics
8. âœ… Populate custom field values

